HEADWORD: Storify
<hw>Sto"ri*fy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Story</ets>
+ <ets>-fy</ets>.]</ety> <def>To form or tell stories of; to narrate or
describe in a story.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
